_sText:
Well, i found some vmf from some time ago... i lowered walls and added displacements. That's mostly it.


This map is BAD when played with just few players, like 4. There are 22 spawns per team for best case scenario :)

Map kinda forces you to look everywhere... and spawn camping dosen't work very well.

There are buyzones at team spawns, and one at the top (each secondary buyzone is looking to other team's primary one). But rushing to top and constantly buying granades will not work.
